title: Kenwood Ham Radio Programming Software
description:
Programming software for Kenwood ham radio equipment. These apps run on Windows...

MCP = Memory Control Program

Radios covered here:

Kenwood TS-2000 - MCP, Remote Control (arpc110)
TH-D7A / TH-D7E and TH-D7A(G) / TH-D7E(G)
TH-F6A
TH-G71A
TH-K2AT
TH-F7E
TM-D700A
TM-G707A
TM-V7A
TS-480
TS-570

Also included is a schematic for the required programming cable. Please note that the TM-D700A and TH-D7A require only a simple serial cable - no level conversion is needed. Warm up your soldering irons and have fun!
